'''越旅行航空'''（{{vie|qn='''Hãng Hàng không Vietravel'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Vietravel Airlines'''}}）是[[越南|越南]]的一間航空公司，該公司是由阮国祺創設的，是越南的第六家航空，第三家私營航空公司，2020年12月中開始運營，1個月內以開闢6條國內航線。經營由[[順化市|順化]]及[[河內|河內]]出發的國內線以及亞洲區域國際線。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://vietnamnews.vn/economy/803716/vietravel-airlines-to-become-countrys-sixth-airline.html|title=Vietravel Airlines to become country's sixth airline|publisher=Vietnam News|date=2020-10-22|accessdate=2020-12-28}}</ref><ref name="founding">{{cite web|url=https://vnexpress.net/thu-tuong-dong-y-lap-hang-hang-khong-vietravel-airlines-4079682.html|title=Thủ tướng đồng ý lập hãng hàng không Vietravel Airlines (Vietnam's PM approved the establishment of Vietravel Airlines)|date = 2020-04-04 |accessdate =2020-12-28 |publisher=VnExpress}}</ref>

==历史==

2020年10月29日自越南交通部取得營運許可，預計年底首航。<ref>{{cite web
|url=https://tuoitre.vn/vietravel-airlines-duoc-cap-giay-phep-bay-20201029163402401.htm|title=Vietravel Airlines được cấp giấy phép bay|date =2020-10-29|accessdate =2020-12-28 |publisher=Tuổi Trẻ News}}</ref>

2020年12月1日正式首航。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tuoitrenews.vn/news/business/20201227/vietravel-airlines-to-launch-commercial-flights-in-january/58486.html|title=Vietravel Airlines to launch commercial flights in January|publisher=Tuoi Tre News|date=2020-12-27|accessdate=2020-12-28}}</ref>

==航點==
越旅行航空的目標是建立国内和东亚航線，含越南冷門航點、亞洲地區。

